{"word":"G4704 - σπουδάζω - spoudázō - spoo-dad'-zo - Do diligence","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σπουδάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>spoudázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>spoo-dad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Do diligence"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"கருத்தோடிரு, ஜாக்கிரதையாயிரு, பிரயத்தனம் பண்ணு - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to hasten, make haste"},{"paragraph":"2. to exert oneself, endeavor, give difference"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4710 - σπουδή - spoudḗ - spoo-day'/4710\">G4710</a>; to <i>use speed</i>, that is, to <i>make effort</i>, <i>be prompt</i> or <i>earnest:</i> - do (give) diligence, be diligent (forward), endeavour, labour, study."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4704 - σπουδάζω - spoudázō - spoo-dad'-zo/4704\">G4704</a>, <a href=\"#/G4705 - σπουδαῖος - spoudaîos - spoo-dah'-yos/4705\">G4705</a>, <a href=\"#/G4706 - σπουδαιότερον - spoudaióteron - spoo-dah-yot'-er-on/4706\">G4706</a>, <a href=\"#/G4707 - σπουδαιότερος - spoudaióteros - spoo-dah-yot'-er-os/4707\">G4707</a>, <a href=\"#/G4708 - σπουδαιοτέρως - spoudaiotérōs - spoo-dah-yot-er'-oce/4708\">G4708</a>, <a href=\"#/G4709 - σπουδαίως - spoudaíōs - spoo-dah'-yoce/4709\">G4709</a>, <a href=\"#/G4710 - σπουδή - spoudḗ - spoo-day'/4710\">G4710</a>"}]}